trans-unit.source: Used to provide design-time support in a visual designer for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList" /> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Se usa para proporcionar compatibilidad en tiempo de diseño en un diseñador visual para el control de servidor web <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList" />.

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: En un diseñador visual, al cambiar de origen a la vista de diseño, el código fuente de marcado que describe el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control se analiza y se crea una versión en tiempo de diseño del control en la superficie de diseño.

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to the markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Al cambiar a vista de origen, el control de tiempo de diseño se conserva en el código fuente de marcado y editar en el marcado de la página Web.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control or a copy of that control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework crea internamente una nueva instancia de la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner> clase cuando se crea el asociado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control o una copia de ese control en la superficie de diseño.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> that contains the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor" /> objects representing the events of the control.
trans-unit.target: La <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> que contiene los objetos <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor" /> que representan los eventos del control.

trans-unit.source: The keys in the <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> are event names.
trans-unit.target: Las claves de <see cref="T:System.Collections.IDictionary" /> son los nombres de evento.

trans-unit.source: Allows the designer to filter the set of events that the associated control will expose at design time.
trans-unit.target: Le permite al diseñador filtrar el conjunto de eventos que el control asociado expondrá en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: Control designers use methods that are derived from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.PostFilterEvents%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method to filter the set of events that the control it is designing will expose through the <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor> object.
trans-unit.target: Diseñadores de controles utilizan métodos que se derivan de la <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.PostFilterEvents%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> método para filtrar el conjunto de eventos que el control que está diseñando va a exponer a través de la <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor> objeto.

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner.PostFilterEvents%2A> method removes the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListControl.SelectedIndexChanged> event from the list that is exposed by the designer.
trans-unit.target: Para el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> (control), el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner.PostFilterEvents%2A> método quita el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListControl.SelectedIndexChanged> eventos de la lista que se expone mediante el diseñador.

trans-unit.source: The keys in the <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> interface are the names of the events.
trans-unit.target: Las claves de la <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> interfaz son los nombres de los eventos.

trans-unit.source: The values in the <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> are objects of type <xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Los valores de la <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> son objetos de tipo <xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>.

trans-unit.source: Overriding the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner.PostFilterEvents(System.Collections.IDictionary)" /> method provides a way to change or remove items within the dictionary of events that are exposed by the designer for this control.
trans-unit.target: Reemplazar el <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner.PostFilterEvents(System.Collections.IDictionary)" /> método proporciona una manera de cambiar o quitar elementos del diccionario de eventos que se exponen por el diseñador para este control.

trans-unit.source: You can directly filter the dictionary that is accessible through the <paramref name="events" /> parameter, or you can leave it unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Se puede filtrar directamente el diccionario que es accesible a través del <paramref name="events" /> parámetro o se puede dejar sin cambios.

trans-unit.source: If you are overriding the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner.PostFilterEvents(System.Collections.IDictionary)" /> method, call the base implementation after you perform your own filtering.
trans-unit.target: Si va a reemplazar el <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner.PostFilterEvents(System.Collections.IDictionary)" /> método, llame a la implementación base después de realizar su propio filtrado.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control that is associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si el diseñador debe utilizar una copia temporal en lugar del control real asociado al diseñador para generar el marcado en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: Always <see langword="true" />.
trans-unit.target: Siempre es <see langword="true" />.

trans-unit.source: Because the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property is always `true`, the designer uses a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control that contains a temporary copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Dado que la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> propiedad es siempre `true`, el diseñador utiliza un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control que contiene una copia temporal del asociado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control para generar el marcado en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control does not affect any persistence for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control no afecta a la persistencia del <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property were to return `false`, the designer would use the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> itself to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Si el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> propiedad fuera a devolver `false`, el diseñador utilizaría asociado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> para generar el marcado en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.source: You can override the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DetailsViewDesigner.UsePreviewControl" /> property to return <see langword="false" /> or to determine its value based on whether the control is marked with a class-level <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Puede invalidar la <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DetailsViewDesigner.UsePreviewControl" /> propiedad para devolver <see langword="false" /> o para determinar su valor en función de si el control está marcado con un nivel de clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute" /> objeto.

trans-unit.source: If the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DetailsViewDesigner.UsePreviewControl" /> property is not overridden, the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner" /> object ignores the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute" />.
trans-unit.target: Si el <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.DetailsViewDesigner.UsePreviewControl" /> no se invalida la propiedad, el <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.BulletedListDesigner" /> objeto omite la <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.SupportsPreviewControlAttribute" />.
